original_title: Rites of Spring: Live at the 9:30 Club
overview: Rites of Spring live at the 9:30 Club during Washington D.C.'s 'Revolution Summer'  - 06/06/1985  Tracklist  1. Drink Deep  2. Hain's Point  3. For Want Of  4. Theme  5. In Silence/Words Away  6. Remainder  7. Spring  8. Deeper Than Inside  9. Nudes  10. End on End  11. All There Is
tagline: I woke up this morning with a piece of past caught in my throat. And then I choked.
title: Rites of Spring: Live at the 9:30 Club
